column1: #Username (Optional. If you haven't defined a user name prefix and leave it empty and - an auto-generated user name will be assigned)
#Number of devices (Optional. If you leave it empty it will be set to 1. Maximal value is 50)
#MAC Address (Optional. Number of Device must be 1 when MAC is mentioned. Valid formats: 12:34:56:78:90:ab, 12-34-56-78-90-ab, 123.456.789.0ab, 1234567890ab)
#Passphrase (if empty, system generated passphrase will be used)
#VLAN ID (if empty, network's default VLAN will be used)

#Passphrase Expiration (If empty, will be considered the value set in linked DPSK Networks. Otherwise,  the valid values: UNLIMITED, ONE_DAY, TWO_DAYS, ONE_WEEK, TWO_WEEKS, ONE_MONTH, SIX_MONTHS, ONE_YEAR, TWO_YEARS)
